media.ext_alt_text: In zero-carbon mission international climate summit, Xie Zhenhua pointed out that although the complex and volatile international political and economic environment has brought difficulties for countries to unite to cope with the climate crisis, the global trend of green and low-carbon transformation and innovation has become irreversible.
